2.11	Pierre_Curzi	Pierre Curzi	Pierre Curzi (born February 11, 1946 in Montreal, Quebec) is an actor, screenwriter and politician in Quebec, Canada. He is the Member of the National Assembly of Quebec (MNA) for the riding of Borduas in the Montérégie region south of Montreal. Elected under the Parti Québécois (PQ) banner, he now sits as an independent.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d0/PierreCurzi.JPG/220px-PierreCurzi.JPG
